I stopped moving.
"Hear that, Goldeneye? It sounds like something is
over there..."
Tails changed to her squirrel form and moved some
bushes apart slightly so she could peek through.
A mosquito-like creature was checking out something...
"Hey Goldeneye? There's something you should maybe
see, here..." Tails whispered.
